a.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/110%2c%e6%98%93%2c772%2c20211202%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,110,易,772,20211202,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"易","JNO":"772","JDATE":"20211202","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}